Country:    USA
Category:   Electronics
Description:Semiconductor switch replacing vacuum tubes
Impact:     Foundation of all modern electronics; miniaturization

Invention:  Microprocessor
Year:       1971
Inventor:   Intel
Country:    USA
Category:   Computing
